io.grpc.stub

Class AbstractStub<S extends AbstractStub<?,?>,C extends AbstractServiceDescriptor<C>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.grpc.stub.AbstractStub<S,C>
  • Type Parameters:
    S - the concrete type of this stub.
    C - the service descriptor type

    public abstract class AbstractStub<S extends AbstractStub<?,?>,C extends AbstractServiceDescriptor<C>>
extends Object
    Common base type for stub implementations.

    This is the base class of the stub classes from the generated code. It allows for reconfiguration, e.g., attaching interceptors to the stub.
